<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870406-0092 </DOCNO><HL> Finanacing Business:Hadson Corp.</HL><DD> 04/06/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> HADSSTOCK MARKET, OFFERINGS (STK) </IN><TEXT>   HADSON CORP. said it sold four million common shares at $8.50 each. Hadson closed at $8.875, up 37.5 cents, in national over-the-counter trading Friday. The Oklahoma City oil and gas producer said proceeds will be used for energy-related acquisitions and working capital. Before the offering, which was increased from 3.75 million shares because of investor interest, Hadson had about 14.5 million shares outstanding, it said. Lead underwriter was Shearson Lehman Brothers Inc. </TEXT></DOC>